  "body": "<center><h3>TerraAdmin</h3></center>\n<hr>\n<center>\n    <a href=\"https://discord.gg/YR7Z5zqyu6\"><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@intergrav/devins-badges@3/assets/cozy/social/discord-plural_vector.svg\" height=\"48\" alt=\"Join the Discord\" /></a>\n  <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/fabric-api\"><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@intergrav/devins-badges@3/assets/cozy/requires/fabric-api_vector.svg\" height=\"48\" alt=\"Requires Fabric API\" /></a>\n  <img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@intergrav/devins-badges@3/assets/cozy/unsupported/forge_vector.svg\" height=\"48\" alt=\"Won't Support Forge\" />\n</center>\n<center>\n    <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/terraadmin\"><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@intergrav/devins-badges@3/assets/cozy/available/modrinth_vector.svg\" height=\"48\" alt=\"Available on Modrinth\" /></a>\n  <a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/terraadmin\"><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@intergrav/devins-badges@3/assets/cozy/available/curseforge_vector.svg\" height=\"48\" alt=\"Available on CurseForge\" /></a>\n</center>\n<hr>\n<br />\nA server-side mod with a suite of useful tools for administrators.\n\n### Features\n📦 Easily open crafting tables, grindstones, etc<br />\n💨 Staff Movement Commands<br />\n🔐 All commands permission locked<br />\n⚙️ Improvements on vanilla commands\n### Planned Features\n• Improvements on vanilla give command<br />\n• Better tp command<br />\n• /staff command<br />\n• Inventory/Enderchest inspect commands<br />",
